These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, azure, green, grey
House: farmhouse, victorian, cape-cod, modern
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, police-officer, social-worker, photographer
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the modern house##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who likes green and the person who likes grey##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the dancer##1
4. the photographer is on the left of the dancer##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the social-worker is the person who likes green##1
7. the victorian house is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | azure | grey   | fuchsia  | green  |
| House   | victorian    | modern    | farmhouse      | cape-cod    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk | cola | lemonade |
| Job     | photographer  | dancer       | police-officer    | social-worker     |

