.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, august, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, architect, pilot, photographer
There 4 different types of food: pepper, peach, corn, lettuce
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo, aristoff, blend
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
3. the person eating lettuce is the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the photographer is between the person eating corn and the prince-smoker##2
6. the blend-smoker is between the photographer and the person eating lettuce##2
7. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1
8. the architect is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
9. the pilot is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | january | december    | august  | november    |
| Job   | musician      | architect  | photographer  | pilot |
| Food           | lettuce      | corn       | peach      | pepper       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo    | blend | aristoff | prince |

