.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: san-francisco, prague, berlin, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, skiing, badminton
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, juice
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, april, october
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is badminton##2
9. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person traveling to berlin and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | prague | berlin     | san-francisco   | marseilles     |
| Sport       | rowing   | handball   | skiing | badminton |
| Beverage         | almond-milk   | fanta | juice       | cola    |
| Birthday   | april    | march | december  | october    |

