.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, 7up, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, soul, country, metal
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, train, roller, scooter
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, card-games, collecting, traveling
 1. the fan soul is on the far right##1
 2. the fan metal is the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
 5. the fan metal is the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the fan soul is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the fan pop is on the right of the fan metal##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is between the person driving the boat and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | coffee  | water | mirinda     | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | metal | pop  | country | soul       |
| Transport           | train       | scooter    | roller      | boat           |
| Hobby         | writing | card-games   | traveling   | collecting         |

