 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the fan d&b##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the fan dubstep is between the colombian and the owner of the rat##2
10. the owner of the turtle is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | blues         | dubstep         | d&b     | hip-hop      |
| Birthday           | may | november | december    | july     |
